SWIRL SEARCH 1.2

New object oriented Connector and Mixers

SWIRL SEARCH 1.2

Cleaning up old connectors

SWIRL SEARCH 1.2

New OO Connector framework, relevancy boost improvements, lowered first check to 3 seconds (from 5)
Moved object list sorting from views.py to model; reverted boost reductions in relevancy processor
Updated docker setup with warning about database deletion upon shutdown
Added note about localhost in docker

SWIRL SEARCH 1.1

Added date_mixer, resolved issue with searchprovider_list, updated documentation images

SWIRL SEARCH 1.1

Revised result wrapper, renamed score to swirl_score, added swirl_rank

SWIRL SEARCH 1.1

Stack results mixer now uses relevancy, round robin refactored out, search performance improvements

SWIRL SEARCH 1.1

Requests_get handle list of items, improve error handling, update banner version

SWIRL SEARCH 1.1

Added support for apache solr, NLResearch.com via rewrite of request_get connector, resolved issues
Release notes 1.0.1, 1.0.2; swirl.py check if 'static' exists in root

Added favicons V1

https://github.com/sidprobstein/swirl-search/issues/9 note they have not been added to the pages yet
Revised Community, Support & Contributing, also TO DO
Switched to Github wiki, restored To Do, clean up user guide, fixed logo for github social
Fixed undeclared var for search 'elastic+amazon', swirl index page, celery log output
